Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  相生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么您来的这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我值班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你来帮忙倒一下垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  绝对不要对大家说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不一定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.55,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,00)\bord15\shad0\be50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N97
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我试着做了果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尝尝看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么突然做这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我之前不是把你的橘子酱用完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐居然做果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你稍微有点女人味了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  你来猜猜这是什么果酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那我就尝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃  难吃  难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃到我都不知道自己在做啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  美绪  有俄罗斯红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫  好烫  除了好烫这茶还好难喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃  难吃  难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  美绪  用果酱冷却舌头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃  难吃  难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃  难吃  难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水  水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！  牛奶奶奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪  那里面我放了剩下的果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么啊  这无与伦比的难吃感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好难吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难吃  难吃  难吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美绪你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太难吃了  我都看到微妙的人生走马灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想到可能会难吃  但没想到居然有这样的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道难吃为什么还要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为总觉得会很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个笨蛋姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道的果酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你肯定放了坏掉的鱼之类的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  差点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解是咸鱼干果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最初也是最后的咸鱼干纪念日
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
